WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 22=

01:49.500 --> 01:50.630
If that's all, you may leave.

01:51.270 --> 01:52.580
Don't just stand here.

01:52.940 --> 01:53.780
How annoying.

01:59.910 --> 02:00.750
Your Grace,

02:01.220 --> 02:02.910
I heard Her Ladyship took a mortal

02:02.910 --> 02:04.140
to the Nine-Square Maze Prison.

02:04.670 --> 02:06.220
She violated the Golden-wall Decrees.

02:06.550 --> 02:07.830
Yeah, Your Grace.

02:08.070 --> 02:09.990
If you hadn't gone there personally,

02:10.230 --> 02:11.790
that mortal would have died.

02:12.830 --> 02:14.700
Her Ladyship knowingly violated the law

02:14.860 --> 02:16.140
and attempted to kill a mortal.

02:16.550 --> 02:17.390
It's...

02:17.400 --> 02:18.700
It's a grave offense.

02:19.230 --> 02:20.580
- That's right.
- Yeah.

02:20.740 --> 02:21.580
Mortal?

02:21.580 --> 02:23.390
There's only one mortal here.

02:24.180 --> 02:25.510
I heard his soul candle

02:25.510 --> 02:26.390
was extinguished.

02:26.620 --> 02:27.620
He survived anyway.

02:28.180 --> 02:29.670
I wonder if Her Grace

02:29.830 --> 02:31.460
did something in the Prison.

02:33.110 --> 02:34.350
Could she be injured?

02:36.270 --> 02:37.110
Your Grace,

02:37.350 --> 02:38.300
it's not appropriate

02:38.300 --> 02:39.140
to shut us out here.

02:39.550 --> 02:41.180
Come out and make a ruling.

02:42.110 --> 02:43.350
Your Grace,

02:43.350 --> 02:44.670
please make a ruling.

03:01.140 --> 03:02.070
How noisy.

03:03.670 --> 03:05.350
Greetings, Your Grace.

03:07.350 --> 03:08.270
Why did you stop?

03:10.350 --> 03:12.250
Her Ladyship took a mortal to the Prison

03:12.550 --> 03:13.470
and violated the law.

03:13.710 --> 03:14.550
Your Grace,

03:14.970 --> 03:15.810
punish her by law.

03:16.420 --> 03:17.550
What do you think, Jiang Ai?

03:18.230 --> 03:19.350
They want you to die.

03:22.620 --> 03:24.670
I did violate the Golden-wall Decrees,

03:24.990 --> 03:26.390
but that mortal didn't die.

03:26.740 --> 03:27.700
According to the law,

03:27.700 --> 03:28.950
I don't deserve to die.

03:29.180 --> 03:30.670
But I'm guilty anyway.

03:31.140 --> 03:31.990
I'll be punished.

03:33.790 --> 03:35.860
Yan Ke, why are you so quiet?

03:37.140 --> 03:37.990
What's your opinion?

03:43.020 --> 03:44.550
As the Left Hand, Jiang Ai

03:44.740 --> 03:46.020
knowingly violated the decrees.

03:46.580 --> 03:48.180
No serious harm was done,

03:48.580 --> 03:50.550
so she shall be flogged thirty times.

03:51.390 --> 03:52.860
As for other offenses,

03:53.140 --> 03:54.110
please determine

03:54.460 --> 03:55.860
by law.

03:59.460 --> 04:00.350
Starting today,

04:01.020 --> 04:02.860
Jiang Ai will reflect on her mistakes.

04:03.510 --> 04:04.580
Her duties will temporarily

04:04.950 --> 04:06.180
be handled by Yan Ke.

04:07.300 --> 04:08.140
From now on,

04:08.740 --> 04:10.300
no one shall trespass

04:10.300 --> 04:11.270
in the Prison.

04:12.510 --> 04:13.620
The flogging

04:16.110 --> 04:18.380
will be executed by Yan Ke.

04:19.550 --> 04:20.670
Immediately.

04:23.150 --> 04:23.990
Yes.

04:26.420 --> 04:28.060
Her Grace still favors His Lordship.

04:29.350 --> 04:30.380
He won't show favoritism

04:31.350 --> 04:33.030
during the flogging.

04:40.420 --> 04:41.860
Do you have any complaints?

04:42.260 --> 04:44.030
Her Grace ordered you to do this.

04:44.590 --> 04:45.740
I believe

04:45.740 --> 04:47.590
you've figured out what she meant.

04:48.180 --> 04:49.260
So I have no complaints.

04:54.910 --> 04:56.230
Everybody is here today.

04:56.420 --> 04:58.060
Then do it now.

04:58.620 --> 05:00.550
Don't spoil Her Grace's mood.

05:18.990 --> 05:20.860
You tried to get rid of me,

05:21.230 --> 05:23.230
but never expected Her Grace
to openly shield me.

05:24.230 --> 05:25.820
Now that your plot has failed,

05:26.350 --> 05:27.190
doesn't it feel bad?

05:37.500 --> 05:38.710
Twenty-eight more lashes.

05:40.150 --> 05:41.620
Your time for abusing me

05:41.620 --> 05:42.460
is almost up.

05:50.790 --> 05:52.420
What happened today

05:54.030 --> 05:56.260
was far worse than I thought.

06:00.180 --> 06:01.030
Her Grace was usually

06:01.030 --> 06:02.110
dependent on Her Ladyship.

06:02.590 --> 06:03.500
But she showed no mercy

06:03.820 --> 06:04.910
in the punishment.

06:06.820 --> 06:08.230
Because Her Grace has no heart.

06:08.230 --> 06:09.420
As if you had one.

06:10.000 --> 06:10.860
Hey.

06:10.860 --> 06:11.990
Don't get me involved.

06:12.470 --> 06:13.310
All of you,

06:14.350 --> 06:15.670
listen up.

06:16.740 --> 06:19.110
Anyone who violates
the Golden-wall Decrees

06:19.710 --> 06:21.110
will end up like this.

06:27.110 --> 06:27.950
Simu.

06:31.030 --> 06:32.150
It's that mortal's voice.

06:36.590 --> 06:37.430
After the flogging,

06:38.180 --> 06:39.020
you may all leave.

06:43.470 --> 06:45.670
Her Ladyship is really suffering.

08:07.670 --> 08:09.260
After all these years,

08:11.230 --> 08:13.820
I was punished again because of him.

08:16.380 --> 08:17.860
Bai Sanxing, I hate you!

08:18.710 --> 08:19.550
I...

08:20.820 --> 08:21.860
(I'll pay you back)

08:22.860 --> 08:24.470
(a hundred times over.)

08:26.710 --> 08:27.990
(I saved you)

08:27.990 --> 08:28.860
(from evil spirits.)

08:29.990 --> 08:31.670
(You should always belong to me.)

08:41.580 --> 08:42.540
Your Ladyship.

09:03.350 --> 09:04.430
May I see you?

09:16.830 --> 09:17.670
Come on in.

09:25.190 --> 09:26.190
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

09:31.430 --> 09:33.190
This is the Glacial Elixir, a tribute

09:33.190 --> 09:34.540
from the Frigid Land last year.

09:34.990 --> 09:36.350
It heals wounds fast.

09:43.620 --> 09:45.070
His Lordship is too cruel.

09:45.900 --> 09:46.950
His Spine Whip

09:47.260 --> 09:48.860
is made of Thunderous Crystal Keel.

09:49.380 --> 09:51.590
When he flogged you,
he even used spiritual energy.

09:52.310 --> 09:53.500
An ordinary spirit

09:53.660 --> 09:54.620
would be annihilated

09:54.620 --> 09:55.830
after just one lash.

09:58.660 --> 10:00.740
He wished I would be annihilated.

10:01.860 --> 10:03.430
Too bad he couldn't kill me.

10:05.660 --> 10:07.660
Now, he's in charge of Xuling Temple,

10:08.230 --> 10:09.860
but everyone is loyal to me.

10:10.430 --> 10:11.860
He won't get anything out of it.

10:14.430 --> 10:16.380
Don't worry too much.

10:18.380 --> 10:19.950
Now he has new problems

10:19.950 --> 10:20.900
to deal with.

10:21.430 --> 10:22.590
He has no time for me.

10:26.620 --> 10:27.740
New problems?

10:30.020 --> 10:31.230
What brings you here?

10:32.430 --> 10:34.260
The mortal's tonic elixir has arrived.

10:34.710 --> 10:36.190
If you can't go,

10:36.190 --> 10:37.310
I'll fetch it for you.

10:37.780 --> 10:38.620
No need.

10:40.430 --> 10:41.660
The more people think

10:41.660 --> 10:43.230
I've fallen,

10:43.660 --> 10:45.430
the more I have to act as usual.

11:00.310 --> 11:01.230
Greetings, Your Grace.

11:01.900 --> 11:02.780
Why did you come here

11:02.780 --> 11:03.620
instead of resting?

11:04.230 --> 11:05.070
Just minor injuries.

11:06.020 --> 11:07.830
His tonic elixir has arrived.

11:08.020 --> 11:09.020
I've brought it to him.

11:13.990 --> 11:14.830
Simu,

11:17.020 --> 11:18.590
in the Nine-Square Maze Prison,

11:18.590 --> 11:20.230
Bai Sanxing suddenly attacked us.

11:20.710 --> 11:22.230
To save me,

11:22.380 --> 11:24.190
he lost his soul candle and got lost.

11:25.020 --> 11:26.310
There, he had a bet with me.

11:26.660 --> 11:28.190
If he made it back alive,

11:28.380 --> 11:30.140
I would tell him about your past.

11:30.740 --> 11:32.110
When he wakes up,

11:32.540 --> 11:34.310
should I honor my bet?

11:36.590 --> 11:37.780
You can tell him.

11:38.230 --> 11:39.070
Yes.

11:43.430 --> 11:44.710
Do you hate Bai Sanxing?

11:53.310 --> 11:54.350
Of course.

11:56.070 --> 11:57.500
That's why I tricked him

11:57.500 --> 11:59.020
into the Nine-Square Maze Prison

11:59.020 --> 12:01.230
and tried so hard to get rid of him.

12:03.780 --> 12:05.470
If someone's body is confined,

12:06.950 --> 12:07.990
he can break free.

12:09.830 --> 12:11.430
But if his heart is held captive,

12:13.230 --> 12:14.540
he'll just willingly

12:14.540 --> 12:15.620
confine himself.

12:16.900 --> 12:17.780
You should know

12:17.780 --> 12:19.110
what's really in your heart.

12:24.900 --> 12:26.430
Then what about you?

12:27.540 --> 12:28.710
These days, you've been

12:28.710 --> 12:30.230
staying by his bed

12:30.500 --> 12:32.140
and taking meticulous care of him.

12:32.620 --> 12:34.380
You even have the morning assembly here.

12:34.540 --> 12:36.070
But you refuse to accept him.

12:37.070 --> 12:38.950
Can you face what's in your own heart?

12:44.260 --> 12:45.100
Simu,

12:45.710 --> 12:47.070
what on earth are you scared of?

13:28.470 --> 13:29.310
How about

13:29.660 --> 13:30.740
you keep me by your side?

13:31.430 --> 13:32.500
Whenever you want to feel,

13:33.430 --> 13:34.380
you can have my senses.

13:35.140 --> 13:35.980
Simu!

13:36.500 --> 13:38.110
For a mortal, staying in the Void

13:38.470 --> 13:39.380
is even more terrifying

13:40.070 --> 13:41.140
than death.

13:42.190 --> 13:43.070
So what?

13:46.500 --> 13:47.990
(Back then, I was weak-willed.)

13:49.500 --> 13:50.470
(I longed for that brief)

13:50.470 --> 13:51.660
(yet sweet companionship.)

13:54.540 --> 13:55.860
I'll definitely treasure

13:55.860 --> 13:56.990
your smart skull.

13:57.500 --> 13:58.340
Foxy,

13:58.660 --> 13:59.990
let me have a taste.

14:02.990 --> 14:04.020
(I yearned for the warmth)

14:04.020 --> 14:05.590
(and softness of the world.)

14:05.990 --> 14:07.620
(So I brought you back to the Void.)

14:10.500 --> 14:12.430
(The Void with endless nights.)

14:15.140 --> 14:16.830
(But you don't belong here, after all.)

14:17.950 --> 14:19.260
(You don't belong in my world.)

14:21.740 --> 14:23.540
(Even if I could have you for a moment,)

14:23.950 --> 14:25.860
(I would inevitably lose you one day.)

14:27.230 --> 14:28.230
(In that case,)

14:29.780 --> 14:31.190
(what's the point of starting?)

14:53.500 --> 14:54.340
Simu.

15:52.660 --> 15:53.500
Only when I'm sick

15:53.500 --> 15:54.990
can I be treated so well.

16:08.140 --> 16:09.230
I'm really awake.

16:18.740 --> 16:19.590
Great.

16:21.380 --> 16:22.220
This is great.

16:23.230 --> 16:24.950
I can still see your smiling face.

16:28.070 --> 16:28.910
Great.

16:32.140 --> 16:33.900
You still want to see this face.

16:45.310 --> 16:46.150
Simu,

16:48.230 --> 16:49.070
I'm sorry.

16:51.640 --> 16:52.540
You've been

16:52.540 --> 16:53.900
through so many terrible memories.

16:56.170 --> 16:57.020
I knew

16:57.020 --> 16:57.990
you hated parting.

16:59.950 --> 17:01.140
But I still let you

17:01.140 --> 17:02.350
watch me grow old.

17:08.470 --> 17:09.500
Sorry, Simu.

17:11.670 --> 17:13.230
I wasn't there for you all the time.

17:17.060 --> 17:18.150
That was an illusion,

17:21.410 --> 17:23.300
but I believe all the joy and delight

17:24.540 --> 17:25.500
were real.

17:27.780 --> 17:29.020
How nice, Simu.

17:30.770 --> 17:31.630
I'm so happy

17:31.630 --> 17:32.990
that you also have feelings for me.

17:35.100 --> 17:36.710
I love being with you too.

17:52.820 --> 17:54.020
If you still like it,

17:56.540 --> 17:58.190
we can buy a house.

17:59.630 --> 18:00.950
With mountains and water around.

18:02.300 --> 18:03.740
We'll plant fruit trees and flowers

18:04.950 --> 18:07.020
behind the mountain.

18:12.260 --> 18:13.670
You love cilantro so much.

18:14.390 --> 18:15.500
We'll just plant cilantro

18:15.500 --> 18:16.500
all along the stream.

18:24.170 --> 18:25.030
I don't understand

18:25.030 --> 18:26.100
why you like this flavor.

18:26.230 --> 18:27.950
Made cilantro-filled moon cakes again?

18:28.910 --> 18:30.300
You love cilantro-filled moon cakes.

18:31.390 --> 18:32.910
Then we'll put more crushed peanuts

18:35.580 --> 18:36.500
and rock sugar.

18:48.100 --> 18:48.940
Simu.

18:50.150 --> 18:50.990
Stop.

18:51.630 --> 18:52.470
Stop that.

18:54.950 --> 18:55.790
Simu.

18:56.190 --> 18:57.190
You shouldn't have said it.

18:57.190 --> 18:58.030
Simu.

19:01.500 --> 19:02.340
Duan Shunxi,

19:04.190 --> 19:05.500
I love being with you.

19:35.470 --> 19:36.340
Simu,

19:38.670 --> 19:39.630
I really,

19:41.340 --> 19:42.470
really like you.

19:51.910 --> 19:53.190
You shouldn't remember.

20:25.260 --> 20:26.710
Neither of us should.

21:53.630 --> 21:54.470
Yan,

21:55.230 --> 21:56.070
have some tea.

21:57.230 --> 21:58.070
Simu,

21:59.190 --> 22:01.230
why did you take a mortal

22:01.230 --> 22:02.300
back to our world

22:03.670 --> 22:05.020
and treat him with special favor?

22:06.300 --> 22:07.430
You even let him live

22:07.430 --> 22:08.580
in the bedchamber

22:08.580 --> 22:09.990
that I had built for you.

22:10.780 --> 22:12.470
This is our home.

22:13.910 --> 22:15.100
No one but me

22:16.150 --> 22:17.540
can stand by your side

22:17.540 --> 22:18.740
and stay with you forever.

22:20.470 --> 22:21.540
Yeah, Yan.

22:23.230 --> 22:24.990
Only you'll stay with me.

22:26.500 --> 22:27.740
Without you in the Void,

22:29.340 --> 22:30.580
I wouldn't feel reassured.

23:12.620 --> 23:15.700
(Zhaomu Pavilion, the Void)

23:42.500 --> 23:43.710
Get up and take the medicine.

23:47.540 --> 23:48.390
Simu.

24:02.870 --> 24:04.150
I'm too weak.

24:05.230 --> 24:06.100
Your Grace,

24:06.470 --> 24:07.580
would you deign to feed me?

24:18.150 --> 24:18.990
Take it.

24:24.150 --> 24:26.020
If one day you have my sense of taste,

24:26.470 --> 24:27.310
you'll know

24:27.870 --> 24:28.710
I hate bitterness.

24:29.390 --> 24:30.430
This medicine

24:31.020 --> 24:31.860
even smells bitter.

24:33.060 --> 24:33.900
Open your mouth.

24:45.710 --> 24:47.150
I guess you often take care of me,

24:47.870 --> 24:49.100
so you're good at feeding me.

24:53.910 --> 24:55.190
You're ticklish and hate bitterness.

24:56.340 --> 24:57.740
Did you see someone in the illusion

24:58.020 --> 24:58.910
who tickled you

24:58.910 --> 24:59.910
and fed you medicine?

25:04.060 --> 25:04.900
Simu.

25:07.150 --> 25:07.990
If you want to know

25:07.990 --> 25:09.100
what I saw in the illusion

25:09.100 --> 25:09.990
of the Prison...

25:11.780 --> 25:12.630
If you do,

25:14.580 --> 25:15.420
I'll tell you.

25:28.910 --> 25:30.190
Like I told you,

25:32.670 --> 25:33.910
before I ended my training

25:35.260 --> 25:36.190
in the All-Knowing,

25:37.500 --> 25:39.470
I helped the High Priest
and the Chong court

25:39.470 --> 25:40.540
do terrible things.

25:41.670 --> 25:43.020
Those memories came back.

25:44.480 --> 25:46.500
I had blood on my hands.

25:47.910 --> 25:48.780
Han Lingqiu

25:50.950 --> 25:52.470
executed people too.

25:55.150 --> 25:57.060
I fed him a memory-erasing potion.

25:59.580 --> 26:01.260
He probably won't remember anything.

26:05.060 --> 26:05.910
That's good.

26:07.630 --> 26:08.740
May he never remember it.

26:16.230 --> 26:17.150
Wake up.

26:18.540 --> 26:19.670
The nightmare is over.

26:20.780 --> 26:21.670
It is?

26:24.100 --> 26:24.940
Yes.

26:26.260 --> 26:27.470
You're my spell bearer.

26:28.500 --> 26:30.470
In this world, no one

26:31.230 --> 26:32.260
can make you experience

26:32.260 --> 26:33.100
a nightmare again.

26:34.990 --> 26:36.060
I will never allow it.

26:43.340 --> 26:44.180
Take it.

26:49.100 --> 26:50.430
It's also part of the nightmare.

26:52.630 --> 26:53.470
I said

26:54.100 --> 26:55.580
no one would make you

26:56.150 --> 26:57.340
experience a nightmare.

26:58.430 --> 26:59.300
But I'm a spirit.

27:00.150 --> 27:01.340
I'm not included.

27:27.670 --> 27:29.260
You're looking good, young man.

27:29.540 --> 27:30.470
It seems Simu

27:30.470 --> 27:31.580
has taken good care of you.

27:33.060 --> 27:34.100
Thank you for your concern.

27:35.230 --> 27:36.340
I've heard

27:37.430 --> 27:38.300
you were punished

27:38.300 --> 27:39.430
because of me.

27:40.060 --> 27:41.230
Sorry to get you involved.

27:43.060 --> 27:45.190
You're well-informed.

27:46.060 --> 27:47.300
Just a few

27:47.300 --> 27:48.470
minor reprimands.

27:48.950 --> 27:50.910
Don't worry.

27:51.710 --> 27:53.430
Sorry for putting you through that.

27:53.670 --> 27:55.100
Some small gifts for you.

27:58.500 --> 27:59.910
Are these all you're giving me?

28:00.670 --> 28:02.060
I remember back in the Prison,

28:02.970 --> 28:03.870
we had a bet.

28:06.540 --> 28:07.740
So you remembered.

28:08.710 --> 28:09.550
This time,

28:10.020 --> 28:11.100
you won the bet.

28:13.390 --> 28:14.670
The duty of the Starhaven Sect

28:14.670 --> 28:16.980
is to maintain the balance
between mortals and spirits.

28:17.100 --> 28:18.150
Simu's mother

28:18.710 --> 28:20.420
was a sorceress in it.

28:20.870 --> 28:22.950
To marry the former sovereign,

28:23.300 --> 28:24.230
she gave up

28:24.230 --> 28:25.500
her position in her sect.

28:25.740 --> 28:27.340
On their wedding day,

28:27.990 --> 28:30.260
the red carpet was rolled out

28:30.540 --> 28:32.630
from the Starhaven Sect
to the Sovereign's Hall.

28:33.990 --> 28:35.580
Flowers danced in the air.

28:36.020 --> 28:37.060
That breathtaking scene

28:37.580 --> 28:38.780
is still vivid in my mind

28:38.780 --> 28:40.100
even now.

28:41.470 --> 28:42.430
After that,

28:43.230 --> 28:45.060
Simu was born.

28:56.340 --> 28:58.060
On the day she was born,

28:58.060 --> 29:00.500
there was a once-in-400-years snowstorm.

29:01.190 --> 29:03.300
- The next day, the chill faded away.
- Simu.

29:03.630 --> 29:04.710
It was warm again.

29:08.820 --> 29:10.100
There's a little rabbit.

29:10.990 --> 29:12.780
She's been gifted since childhood.

29:13.390 --> 29:14.500
When she was young,

29:14.500 --> 29:16.470
she was just as powerful as me.

29:17.870 --> 29:19.780
But she seldom came to the Void.

29:20.630 --> 29:22.820
Her parents took her to the Mortal World

29:22.820 --> 29:24.990
- where she lived as a mortal.
- There. The fish.

29:24.990 --> 29:25.830
It swam past.

29:26.150 --> 29:27.230
Yeah. That's it.

29:27.470 --> 29:28.310
Go catch it.

29:29.390 --> 29:30.300
I got it!

29:33.670 --> 29:35.390
Simu, have all my candy.

29:35.390 --> 29:36.430
Thank you, everyone.

29:36.430 --> 29:37.820
- Take my toys too.
- Enough.

29:37.820 --> 29:38.390
All right.

29:38.390 --> 29:39.870
When we have time, we'll come back.

29:39.870 --> 29:41.500
Simu was a bit different

29:41.500 --> 29:42.430
from ordinary mortals.

29:42.950 --> 29:44.870
But they lived a carefree life.

29:45.580 --> 29:46.540
She and her parents

29:46.540 --> 29:48.280
helped mortals as much as they could.

29:48.280 --> 29:48.870
We should go.

29:48.870 --> 29:50.540
They made good connections with mortals.

29:50.540 --> 29:51.540
Why are they so warm?

29:52.190 --> 29:53.540
Because they love us.

29:55.060 --> 29:56.390
Because they love us.

29:58.260 --> 29:59.500
These mortals

29:59.500 --> 30:01.100
love their families,

30:01.470 --> 30:02.310
their sweethearts,

30:02.580 --> 30:03.500
and their friends.

30:04.540 --> 30:05.500
They even love

30:05.500 --> 30:06.820
this vast world.

30:07.950 --> 30:09.060
See you!

30:11.100 --> 30:12.300
- At that time...
- See you!

30:12.300 --> 30:14.340
- She had many friends and relatives.
- See you.

30:14.340 --> 30:15.190
See you!

30:15.190 --> 30:17.390
- She thought they would meet again.
- See you.

30:17.740 --> 30:18.910
- She didn't know.
- See you!

30:19.390 --> 30:20.990
There were some people

30:20.990 --> 30:22.430
she would never meet again.

30:22.990 --> 30:24.100
"See you"

30:24.950 --> 30:26.020
means "never see you."

30:26.540 --> 30:27.380
Father,

30:28.260 --> 30:29.670
so this is death?

30:37.300 --> 30:38.190
Your mother...

30:41.910 --> 30:43.190
Her destiny is sealed.

30:45.150 --> 30:46.500
She did everything she could

30:48.190 --> 30:49.870
to stay with us until now.

30:57.260 --> 30:58.870
In the end, you and I have no one

31:00.670 --> 31:01.670
but each other.

31:05.870 --> 31:07.390
This is quite sad.

31:49.260 --> 31:50.300
But Father,

31:52.990 --> 31:54.630
you broke your promise too.

32:09.340 --> 32:11.340
After the former sovereign passed away,

32:11.470 --> 32:13.430
the Void fell into chaos.

32:14.740 --> 32:16.060
All the spirits here

32:16.190 --> 32:17.390
coveted

32:17.390 --> 32:18.630
the throne.

35:42.340 --> 35:47.190
♪Spirits are intoxicated♪

35:47.360 --> 35:51.010
♪With obsessions♪

35:54.030 --> 35:58.970
♪Forget the form to achieve♪

35:59.170 --> 36:02.910
♪Yet I can't♪

36:05.650 --> 36:10.500
♪Today, a home is granted♪

36:11.350 --> 36:16.680
♪Joy without grief♪

36:17.210 --> 36:22.020
♪Lanterns light the empty delusions♪

